T1  - More on the time consistency of monetary policy
AU  - Nicolini, Juan Pablo
JO  - Journal of Monetary Economics
VL  - 41
IS  - 2
SP  - 333
EP  - 350
PY  - 1998
DA  - 1998/02/27/
SN  - 0304-3932
